instruction: Please analyze the performance of the Green Index and the Fossil Fuel Index within our analysis period.
output: Based on our analysis, the performance of the Green Index was roughly in line with the market and had an annualized excess return of -0.3%, while the Fossil Fuel Index had an excess return of -16.2%. At the same time, oil prices fell by 17.4% on an annualized basis. Therefore, it can be concluded that the performance of the Green Index is similar to the market, while the Fossil Fuel Index mainly reflects the trend of oil prices. However, further research on this timeframe could provide more discoveries.
